&lt;p&gt;MinIO is the data and memory foundation for enterprise AI. Built for the speed, scale, and economics that AI and analytics demand, AIStor and MemKV unify every layer of the data stack, from agentic and inference context memory to tables and objects across core, edge, and cloud. Trusted by 77% of the Fortune 100, MinIO is redefining how AI factories, intelligent applications, and autonomous agents secure, persist, and unlock the full value of their data.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re building the complete data stack for AI — exascale object store, table&amp;nbsp;store, agent memory, and brain: every layer of how AI stores, retrieves, and&amp;nbsp;thinks over data. Hard problems with no existing answers. Bring your own.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You’ll own problems end-to-end — the kind most&amp;nbsp;engineering teams never get close to. No ticket queues,&amp;nbsp;no standups, no permission. Just you, the codebase, and&amp;nbsp;a team of people who care as much as you do. Everyone&amp;nbsp;here is an IC, an architect, or a lead — most are all three.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Skills and Experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Deep OS internals. Networking from the socket layer up.&amp;nbsp;Strong opinions on memory, concurrency, and&amp;nbsp;correctness — and the humility to revise them. You’ve&amp;nbsp;debugged something no one else could reproduce.You’ve read source code not because you had to, but&amp;nbsp;because it was bothering you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Competencies:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluent in ≥2 languages, honest about tradeoﬀs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You debug by understanding, not by guessing&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Grit: you start hard things and finish them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curiosity you genuinely can’t switch oﬀ&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Low ego, extremely high standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You write code the next engineer respects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operating Systems, Networking, Systems Programming, Distributed Systems, Storage Engines, Vector/Graph Retrieval, Low -Latency I/O, and Protocol Design&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;MinIO Engineering Culture:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;All leads, architects and ICs — no managers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Full ownership from day one, no permission&lt;br&gt;needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Decisions made by the people doing the work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craftsmanship is a first-class engineering&lt;br&gt;concern&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;No sprints. No standups. No Jira.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
